        =
        0
        ,
        …
        ,
        n
        −
        1.
      
    
    {\displaystyle x_{k}=\cos \left({\frac {\pi (k+1/2)}{n}}\right),\quad k=0,\ldots ,n-1.}
  Similarly, the roots of Un are:

  
    
      
        
