    {\displaystyle U_{m}(x)\,U_{n}(x)=\sum _{k=0}^{n}\,U_{m-n+2k}(x)=\sum _{\underset {\text{ step 2 }}{p=m-n}}^{m+n}U_{p}(x)~.}
  for m ≥ n.
For n = 2 this recurrence reduces to:

  
    
      
        
          U
          
